# Design

### A6000

001-DiM-S-2: 两个mamba block

003-DiM-S-2: 一个mamba block 替换掉self-attn

004-DiM-S-2: 每个layer仅有一个mamba block，# layers x 2

005-DiM-S-2:

* Bi-mamba + MLP

* 但是routing最后没有做mlp-merging, 而是简单的avg

006-DiM-S-2:

* same with 005, 但是forward & backward branch的out_proj非共享

* 💥 13 epochs loss nan

### DGX

001-DiM-S-2: 借鉴ViM实现的bi-mamba [38.3M; train step/sec: 6.20]. 

* Bi-mamba + MLP

* Lr x 5 -> 5e-4: 005-DiM-S-2

002-DiM-S-2: 借鉴ViM实现的bi-mamba [36.7M; train step/sec: 3.94]. 

* Bi-mamba x 2

006-DiM-S-2: 

* refer to ViM bi-mamba; [38.3M; train step/sec: 6.20]. 

* also, refer to Hamdard product when routing 'forward' & 'backward' branches in BiGS

007-DiM-S-2: 

* 005基础上，layers 12->10, # params: 32.2M

008-DiM-B-2:

* Bi-mamba + MLP; Lr x 5 -> 5e-4

* Layers: 12 -> 11
